WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.696
It came out of me: "You love me the way you love your remote control.

00:00:02.736 --> 00:00:05.466
"As long as I switch every time you press one of my buttons."

00:00:06.536 --> 00:00:07.466
That's terrific.

00:00:07.536 --> 00:00:10.766
People that talk in metaphors oughta shampoo my crotch.

00:00:12.646 --> 00:00:15.936
- Eat up.
- Stay there. I've got your money.

00:00:16.016 --> 00:00:18.136
- No, pay me next week.
- No, I owe you.

